The intent of this section is to document the APS software architecture. The following diagrams are just examples and do not necessary reflect the current APS design. These are to get agreement with TMT on the concepts, which will lead to agreements on stereotypes and attributes.

 

The governing documents for the TMT software architecture are the following: https://docushare.tmt.org/docushare/dsweb/Services/Document-24356
and: https://docushare.tmt.org/docushare/dsweb/Services/Document-24358
